<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    {{ block "header" . }} {{ end }}
    {{ block "conf_seo" . }} {{ end }}
  </head>
<body>
{{ block "conf_nav" .Conf }} {{ end }}
<section id="intro" class="lg:mb-20 lg:pb-20">
 <div class="relative">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="relative z-10 pt-14 lg:w-full lg:max-w-2xl">
        <svg class="absolute inset-y-0 right-8 hidden h-full w-80 translate-x-1/2 transform fill-white lg:block" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <polygon points="0,0 90,0 50,100 0,100" />
        </svg>

        <div class="relative px-6 pt-12 pb-12 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-12 lg:px-8 lg:pt-12 lg:pb-24 lg:pr-0">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-xl">
            <div class="hidden sm:mb-10 sm:flex">
              <div class="relative rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-500 ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 hover:ring-gray-900/20">
                Get involved in the cutting edge of bitcoin. <a href="/sponsor" target="_blank" class="whitespace-nowrap font-semibold {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color"><span class="absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true"></span>Become a Sponsor<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl"><span class="font-bitcoin">bitcoin++</span> goes dark</h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">{{ .Conf.OGFlavor }}</p>
            <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">{{ .Conf.Location }} | {{ .Conf.Venue }} | {{ .Conf.DateDesc }}</p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
              <a href="#tickets" class="rounded-md {{ .Conf.Tag }} px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2">Get Your All Conf Pass</a>
            </div>
            {{ template "conf_countdown" .Conf }}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-30 mt-6 sm:mt-8 lg:absolute lg:inset-x-0 lg:bottom-0 lg:mt-0 lg:translate-y-[calc(50%+20px)]">
      {{ template "sponsor_banner" . }}
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2">
      <img class="aspect-[3/2] object-cover lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full lg:w-full" src="/static/img/{{ .Conf.Tag }}/leading.avif" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="bitcoin-korea-conference" class="bg-[#101018] pt-24 pb-10 lg:pt-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <a href="https://www.bitcoinkoreaconference.com/en"
       target="_blank"
       rel="noopener noreferrer"
       class="group relative block overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/15 bg-[#15122a]/90 px-6 py-6 shadow-2xl shadow-fuchsia-950/30 ring-1 ring-white/10 transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-fuchsia-300/50 sm:px-8">
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-[#7BA4F7] via-[#C084FC] to-[#F0ABFC]"></div>
      <div class="absolute -right-16 -top-20 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[#C084FC]/25 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-24 left-12 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-[#7BA4F7]/20 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
        <div class="relative max-w-3xl">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-[#F0ABFC]">Stay in Seoul after bitcoin++</p>
          <img src="/static/img/seoul/miniconf_wide.jpeg"
               alt="Bitcoin Korea Conference"
               class="mt-3 h-auto w-full max-w-2xl rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black object-contain shadow-lg shadow-black/30" />
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-white/75">
            Korea's premier Bitcoin conference runs November 7-8, 2026 at COEX Samsung, with Bitcoin education, workshops, a Lightning market, and community building.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative flex shrink-0 flex-col gap-3 text-sm text-white sm:flex-row sm:items-center lg:flex-col lg:items-end">
          <div class="rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-white/85">Nov 7-8, 2026</div>
          <div class="rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-white/85">COEX Samsung</div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#7BA4F7] via-[#C084FC] to-[#F0ABFC] px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-fuchsia-900/30 transition group-hover:opacity-90">
            Visit event site <span aria-hidden="true" class="ml-1">&rarr;</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="about">
  <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white pt-14 pb-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:flex lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white py-10 sm:py-10">
        <h2 class="text-center mt-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Why Privacy?</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Transacting privately is a cornerstone of freedom from tyranny and control. Bitcoin is an important tool at the forefront of freedom to transact peer to peer. It's transparency and auditability however are often at odds with the goal of perserving an individual's right to privacy. Join us in Seoul this coming November for a deep dive into the forefront of privacy and peer to peer exchange, both on-chain and off.</p>
        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 overflow-hidden lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4 mt-12">
            <div>
                <time datetime="2021-08" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color">
                 Privacy + Public Good
            </div>
            <div>
                <time datetime="2021-12" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color">
              Freedom to Transact
            </div>
            <div>
                <time datetime="2022-02" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color">
              Censorship Resistance
            </div>
            <div>
                <time datetime="2022-12" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color">
             Open Source
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="venue">
<div class="overflow-hidden bg-white pt-14 pb-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:flex lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:min-w-full lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none lg:gap-y-8">
      <div class="lg:col-end-1 lg:w-full lg:max-w-lg lg:pb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Going Dark in {{ .Conf.Location }}</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">Experience Seoul + send a silent payment in person</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600"><span class="font-bitcoin">bitcoin++</span> is excited to be continuing our privacy editions in Seoul, South Korea</p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex">
          <a href="#tickets" class="rounded-md {{ .Conf.Tag }} px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2">Get Your All Access Pass<span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-end gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:contents">
        <div class="w-0 flex-auto lg:ml-auto lg:w-auto lg:flex-none lg:self-end">
          <img src="/static/img/{{ .Conf.Tag }}/one.jpg" alt="" class="aspect-[7/5] w-[37rem] max-w-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="contents lg:col-span-2 lg:col-end-2 lg:ml-auto lg:flex lg:w-[37rem] lg:items-start lg:justify-end lg:gap-x-8">
          <div class="order-first flex w-64 flex-none justify-end self-end lg:w-auto">
            <img src="/static/img/{{ .Conf.Tag }}/two.jpg" alt="" class="aspect-[4/3] w-[24rem] max-w-none flex-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="flex w-96 flex-auto justify-end lg:w-auto lg:flex-none">
            <img src="/static/img/{{ .Conf.Tag }}/three.jpg" alt="" class="aspect-[7/5] w-[37rem] max-w-none flex-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:block sm:w-0 sm:flex-auto lg:w-auto lg:flex-none">
            <img src="/static/img/{{ .Conf.Tag }}/four.jpg" alt="" class="aspect-[4/3] w-[24rem] max-w-none rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 object-cover">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
    <iframe title="{{ .Conf.Venue }}" aria-lable="{{ .Conf.Venue }}" 
    class="mt-12"
	  width="100%"
	  height="500px"
	  frameborder="0" style="border:0"
	  referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
	  src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyBs_ErgLEfaa9HBJfMzdm45JPhQgdPAMwc&amp;q=페이지명동&amp;zoom=16"
	  allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white py-10 sm:py-10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-xl">Where to Stay</h3>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">The conference will be held at the Page Project in Myeong-Dong, Seoul, South Korea. Here are some other hotels nearby.</p>
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 overflow-hidden lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4 mt-12">
      {{ $tag := .Conf.Tag }}
      {{ range .Hotels }}
      {{ if .Img }}
      <div>
        <time datetime="2021-08" class="flex items-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 {{ $tag }}-color">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 4 4" class="mr-4 h-1 w-1 flex-none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="2" cy="2" r="2" fill="currentColor" />
          </svg>
	      {{ .Type }}
          <div class="absolute -ml-2 h-px w-screen -translate-x-full bg-gray-900/10 sm:-ml-4 lg:static lg:ml-8 lg:-mr-6 lg:w-auto lg:flex-auto lg:translate-x-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </time>
        <a href="{{ .URL }}" target="_blank">
            <img src="{{ spacesURL .Img }}" height="350" width="100%" class="mt-12 w-full max-h-xl rounded-xl" />
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">{{ .Name }}</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">{{ .Desc }}</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      {{ end }}
      {{ end }}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
<section id="speakers">
<div class="bg-white py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Who's Coming</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600"><span class="font-bitcoin">bitcoin++</span>'s third privacy edition will have an all-star lineup of devs, privacy advocates, and cryptographers from around the globe.</p>
    </div>
    <ul role="list" class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
      {{ range .EventSpeakers }}
        {{ block "speaker" . }} {{ end }}
      {{ end }}
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
{{ if .Conf.HasAgenda }}
<section id="agenda">
  <div class="bg-white py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Conference Agenda</h2>
      </div>
      {{ if .Conf.HasEnded }}
        {{ template "agenda_past" . }}
      {{ else }}
        {{ template "agenda_active" . }}
      {{ end }}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{{ end }}
{{ if not .Conf.HasEnded }}
<section id="tickets">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Get Your All Conference Pass</h2>
      {{ if .Tix }}
        {{ if eq .Tix.USD .MaxTix.USD }}
           <!-- max ticket reached -->
           {{ if lt .TixLeft 40 }}
              <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">Only <span class="text-zinc-900 font-bold">{{ .TixLeft }}</span> tickets are left!</p>
           {{ end }}
        {{ else }}
          <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">Ticket prices go up on <span class="taipei-color">{{ .Tix.Expires.DateDesc }}</span>
          {{ if lt .TixLeft 40 }}
          or after 
            <span class="text-zinc-900 font-bold">{{ .TixLeft }}</span> more tickets are sold!</p>
          {{ else }}
            </p>
          {{ end }}
        {{ end }}
      {{ else }}
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">This event is sold out! 🙈</p>
      {{ end }}
    </div>
  </div>
  {{ if .Tix }}
  <div class="relative isolate bg-white pb-24 px-6 sm:pb-32 lg:px-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 -top-3 -z-10 transform-gpu overflow-hidden px-36 blur-3xl" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="mx-auto w-[72.1875rem]" viewBox="0 0 1155 678">
        <path fill="url(#083c110e-60c8-42bb-a9db-29bba74cc569)" fill-opacity=".3" d="M317.219 518.975L203.852 678 0 438.341l317.219 80.634 204.172-286.402c1.307 132.337 45.083 346.658 209.733 145.248C936.936 126.058 882.053-94.234 1031.02 41.331c119.18 108.451 130.68 295.337 121.53 375.223L855 299l21.173 362.054-558.954-142.079z" />
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="083c110e-60c8-42bb-a9db-29bba74cc569" x1="1155.49" x2="-78.208" y1=".177" y2="474.645" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop stop-color="#9089FC" />
            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#FF80B5" />
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl lg:max-w-7xl">
      <div class="isolate mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-md grid-cols-1 gap-y-8 sm:mt-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">

      {{ if gt .Tix.Local 0 }}
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 xl:p-10 lg:mt-8 lg:rounded-r-none">
         <div>
          <h3 id="tier-fiat" class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-green">Locals Only</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-2">
            {{ if ne .MaxTix.Local .Tix.Local}}
            <span class="line-through text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-300">{{ .Tix.Symbol }}{{ .MaxTix.Local }}{{ .Tix.PostSymbol }} {{ .Tix.Currency }}</span>
            {{ end }}
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">{{ .Tix.Symbol }}{{ .Tix.Local }}{{ .Tix.PostSymbol }} {{ .Tix.Currency }}</span>
            <span class="text-base text-gray-500">/ticket</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Are you a local Korean? This ticket tier is for you! <span class="font-bold">Note: proof of citizenship will be required at check-in.</span></p>
          <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 sm:mt-10">
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              All conference pass
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Unlimited access to workshops
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Access to all parties + excursions
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
        Swag bag with t-shirts and other goodies
            </li>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            Compete for hackathon prizes
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="/tix/{{ .Tix.ID }}+local+btc" aria-describedby="tier-bitcoin" class="mt-8 block rounded-md py-2.5 px-3.5 font-semibold focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-bitcoin sm:mt-10 bg-bitcoin" style="background: #FF8A00">{{ block "btcbutton" . }}{{ end }}</a>
        <a href="/tix/{{ .Tix.ID }}+local+fiat" aria-describedby="tier-fiat" class="mt-2 block rounded-md py-2.5 px-3.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 sm:mt-4 ring-1 ring-inset {{ .Conf.Tag }}">Pay with Fiat</a>
      </div>
      {{ end }}
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 xl:p-10 lg:z-10 lg:rounded-b-none">
        <div>
          <h3 id="tier-bitcoin" class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-bitcoin">Pay with Bitcoin</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-2">
            {{ if ne .MaxTix.BTC .Tix.BTC }}
            <span class="line-through text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-300">{{ .Tix.Symbol }}{{ .MaxTix.BTC }}{{ .Tix.PostSymbol }} {{ .Tix.Currency }}</span>
            {{ end }}
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900">{{ .Tix.Symbol }}{{ .Tix.BTC }}{{ .Tix.PostSymbol }} {{ .Tix.Currency }}</span>
            <span class="text-base text-gray-500">/ticket</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Spend bitcoin, save money.</p>
          <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 sm:mt-10">
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              All conference pass
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Unlimited access to workshops 
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Discounted rate for paying in bitcoin
            </li>

            <li class="flex gap-x-3">
              <svg class="h-6 w-5 flex-none {{ .Conf.Tag }}-color" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Access to all parties + excursions
